<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span class="c2">(٧٩١)</span> السؤال: مَنْ أصابهُ شيءٌ من<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>